title: 129: The Fast & Easy Episode
itunes:title: The Fast & Easy Episode
description: In this episode, Lisa tells all about the new Hungry Girl cookbook, Fast & Easy!! This is her 14th book and she has lots to say about her fastest and easiest recipes EVER! Plus, make sure to listen all the way through for a chance to win some HG collectibles! What are you waiting for?? Push play now, and then when you’re done, head on over to the Foodcast page for a list of everything mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: It’s finally here, the brand-new Hungry Girl cookbook!! Lisa has the 411 on what’s inside…
